<br>
The reason this change was made is because attending a raid/event is generally the most time consuming way to earn points in this system so we feel a player should be rewarded more points for doing this. The reason logging in to EQ was changed to 1 point is to keep balance between ways to earn points that require getting on EQ and ways to earn points without having to get on EQ.<br>
<br>
Changes made to system are highlighted yellow in the original Divine Points System post.<br>
<br>
Post any feedback on this change here if you like. <p><br>
